org.apache.hadoop.hbase.replication.regionserver

类 HFileReplicator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.hbase.replication.regionserver.HFileReplicator

  • @InterfaceAudience.Private
public class HFileReplicator
extends Object
    It is used for replicating HFile entries. It will first copy parallely all the hfiles to a local staging directory and then it will use (LoadIncrementalHFiles to prepare a collection of LoadIncrementalHFiles.LoadQueueItem which will finally be loaded(replicated) into the table of this cluster.

    • 嵌套类概要

      嵌套类 
      限定符和类型 类和说明
      private class  HFileReplicator.Copier
      This class will copy the given hfiles from the given source file system to the given local file system staging directory.
